reviewText:
If you're looking for a hard simplistic puzzle  game, get this one!

Pros:
- calm, relaxing music;
- decent art, made me remember some SNES games;
-  simple gameplay, you won't need more than a seashell's IQ to make the bird move;

Cons (maybe):
- I do hope you're smarter than a seashell to make the bird move CORRECTLY;

Altough difficult, it's very enjoyable tasting this alternative puzzle game.
Get ready to spend a LOT of time in some stages. :)
